Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:58.18,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:42.01,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快瞧 那邊有人浮上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:43.31,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快開船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:46.11,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:47.97,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:50.17,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:34.33,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今我仍舊在這裡守望著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.69,0:23:39.25,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守望著光他們所在的這片大海
